  <body>
  
    <section name="Map reads with gsnap step">

      <p>This step allow to map read with the Gsnap mapper program.</p>  

      <ul>
    <li><b>Internal name</b>: gsnap</li> 
        <li><b>Available</b>: Only in local mode.</li>
        <li><b>Input</b>: filtered reads (e.g. <code>filtered_reads_1.fq</code>).</li>
        <li><b>Output</b>: alignments in SAM format (e.g. <code>mapper_results_1.sam</code>)</li>   
    <br/>
        <li><b>Optional parameters</b>:</li>
    <table>
                <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th><th>Description</th><th>Default value</th></tr>
                <tr><td>mapperArguments</td><td>string</td><td>Mapper additional command line arguments</td><td>-N 1</td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <br/>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </body>
  
